Can you believe it has been 10 years since we landed on a comet? 

On 12 November 2014, after a ten-year journey through the Solar System and over 500 million kilometres from home, our Rosetta missions lander Philae made history by touching down on a comet for the first time. https://t.co/ee4jyzhwZ2
